mendations.</li>\r\n</ol>','Caanit Gas','We were engaged  to review the Operations of Caanit Gas and restructure it for efficient performance and profitability','publish','closed','closed','','caanit-gas','','','2016-07-18 16:08:22','2016-07-18 16:08:22','',0,'http://bolag.dev/?post_type=projects&#038;p=39',0,'projects','',0),(40,1,'2016-07-18 16:12:16','2016-07-18 16:12:16','<strong>DESIGN AND CONSTRUCTION OF A PETROLEUM STORAGE DEPOT </strong><strong>LOCATION</strong>\r\nBolag Resources Limited in Partnership with Nathus Consult supervised the Design and Construction of Lister Petroleum Storage Depot at 23 Creek Road Apapa Lagos\r\nLister Oil is an Independent Oil Marketing Company with a fleet of PETROL STATIONS. The Depot Project was designed to have nine storage Tanks with a total Capacity of 42,000 metric tons for Petrol, Diesel (AGO) and Kerosene.\r\n\r\n<strong><u>WORK SCOPE</u></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Supervised the design of the Petroleum Storage Depot.</li>\r\n 	<li>Reviewed the design Drawings with the Client</li>\r\n 	<li>Advised Lister Oil on the Regulatory requirements for the design and construction of Petroleum Storage Depot.</li>\r\n 	<li>Liaise with all Regulatory Agencies to obtain necessary approvals as required.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Department of Petroleum Resources</li>\r\n 	<li>Lagos Town Planning Authority.</li>\r\n 	<li>Lagos State Environmental Ministry.</li>\r\n 	<li>Fire office.</li>\r\n 	<li>Police</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li> Prepare Bill of Quantity</li>\r\n 	<li> Called for Quotation</li>\r\n 	<li> Analyzed Quotations submitted by Contractors</li>\r\n 	<li> Recommended successful contractors to the client</li>\r\n 	<li> Monitored daily construction activities\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Soil Tests/Pre Soil improvement</li>\r\n 	<li>Soil Tests Post soil improve met</li>\r\n 	<li>Foundation and monitoring appropriate Tests</li>\r\n 	<li>Tank construction /welding and all recommended Tests</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>Coordinated project meetings with the Contractors</li>\r\n 	<li>Carried out daily inspection of construction works</li>\r\n 	<li>Coordinated the activities of all the Contractors</li>\r\n 	<li>Vetted Measured Works and recommended payments as per Agreement</li>\r\n 	<li>Arranged Pre-commissioning inspection of the Depot</li>\r\n 	<li>Process application for License to operate the Depot</li>\r\n 	<li>Prepared project progress reports for Lister Oil Management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><u>THE PETROLEUM STORAGE DEPOT FACILITIES</u></strong>\r\nStorage Tanks with a total capacity of 42,000 metric Tons\r\nTank farm bund wall\r\nProducts\r\nLoading Gantry\r\nPiping networks\r\nFire Pump House\r\nSwitchgear Room\r\nGate house\r\nLaboratory\r\nOffices\r\nJetty\r\nFire Hydrant system\r\nBorehole and water Treatment plant\r\nPumps\r\nElectrical works','Lister Oil','Design and construction of a petroleum storage depot in partnership with Nathus Consult supervised the Design and Construction of Lister Petroleum Storage Depot at 23 Creek Road Apapa Lagos ','publish','closed','closed','','lister-oil','','','2016-07-18 16:12:17','2016-07-18 16:12:17','',0,'http://bolag.dev/?post_type=projects&#038;p=40',0,'projects','',0),(41,1,'2016-07-18 16:25:53','2016-07-18 16:25:53','<div id=\"yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1467277768465_521011\"><span id=\"yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1467277768465_521012\">Bolag Resources (BR) Oil &amp; Gas in partnership with </span><a href=\"http://www.3lpgas.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><b id=\"yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1467277768465_521013\"><span id=\"yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1467277768465_521014\">RV Impianti – 3LP Gas Group of Italy</span></b></a><span id=\"yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1467277768465_521015\"> delivers LPG &amp; Natural Gas products and services to the Nigeria market. Our range of service and products includes design and construction LPG plant, supply and installation of LPG storage tanks, LPG skid systems, LPG dispensers, LPG pumps and gauges.  </span></div>\r\n<div id=\"yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_14672